Question: What device is made of the same material as the hair clip that is lying on top of the bed?

Reference Answer: cell phone

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n293477.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='hair clip')
IMAGE0=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='device')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the hair clip made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the device made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
